request.description:
Get all approved rides with default pagination (page 1, limit 20).

**Response shape:**
```json
{
  "data": [Ride[]],
  "meta": { "total", "page", "limit", "totalPages" }
}
```

Only returns rides with `status: APPROVED`.

Get all approved stories, sorted by most recent. Pinned stories always come first.

**Response shape:**
```json
{
  "data": [Story[]],
  "meta": { "total", "page", "limit", "totalPages" }
}
```
